# --- Open-source: internal artifacts (kept locally, removed from the remote) ---
# Every path below was already tracked; the cleanup ran `git rm --cached` on each
# so it leaves the public remote while staying on local disk. The leading-slash
# ANCHORING is deliberate: a bare `.claude/` would also match the SEPARATE
# app/.claude/ design-studio skills tree, which we KEEP public.

# Root agent-tooling skills tree (~22MB) and its lockfile.
/.claude/
/skills-lock.json

# Hackathon deck (fonts, frames, deck HTML/CSS, build scripts, model copies).
/slides/

